Introduction

  The IRC notifier plugin provides an IRC based notifier implementation.

Usage

  Example configuration:
  
+--
<notifier name="irc">
	<irc:irc xmlns:irc="urn:be:e-contract:jwatchdog:notifier:irc:1.0"
		server="irc.freenode.net" name="jwatchdog" channel="#jwatchdog" />
</notifier>
+--

  Please notice that connecting to an IRC server can take a while.

